::Ramulus::

Ramulus looked at Fliq, his face a bit white. The Maximal was not used to 
space travel, having come online on earth and never having left it. He 
blinks, his mind recovering from the lift-off. He grins.

"Being the hero and saving femms," he brags, "Some Pred was following a new 
Maximal, I shot him down and saved her."

It wasn't like him to brag, but the feeling from lifting off wasn't very 
good, and he needed something to take his mind off of throwing up.
